      "content": "\"there are no rules saying you must feel whole again before you are allowed to stop struggling\"... that's a heavy thing to say. it almost sounds like you're saying i don't have to keep fighting this. it's just so exhausting to wake up every morning to a world that's missing him. it feels like the struggle is the only thing actually left.",
